description:
H4: src/lib/tailwind-utils.ts has three functions (getEmbossShadow, withActiveShadow, withDataStateShadow) that each contain identical 8-line shadow string building logic. Combined total: 24 shadow string definitions across 3 functions when there are only 8 unique shadow values. Every shadow change requires edits in 3 separate places.

```tsx
// Appears verbatim 3 times across 3 functions
if (type === 'out') {
  return size === 'standard'
    ? 'shadow-emboss-out-light dark:shadow-emboss-out-dark'
    : 'shadow-emboss-out-light-sm dark:shadow-emboss-out-dark-sm'
}
```

Fix: Extract a shared `getShadowString(type, size)` helper and call it from all three functions.
